import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { AppService } from "./app.service"; @Component({ selector: 'app-root', templateUrl: './app.component.html', styleUrls: ['./app.component.css'] }) export class AppComponent implements OnInit { title = 'TestMultimodal'; public datos: any = []; constructor(private _appService: AppService) {} ngOnInit(): void { this._appService.getDatos().subscribe(datos => { this.datos = datos; }) } }
